June 09, 1994 was a Thursday and it was the 160th day of the year 1994 in the Gregorian calendar.

June 09, 1994 can also be written as 6/9/1994 in the US and as 9/6/1994 in UK and Europe.

Moon phase

The moon phase on June 09, 1994 was New Moon.

The moon phase refers to the appearance of the Moon in the night sky on June 09, 1994 and is determined by the portion of the Moon's illuminated surface that is visible from Earth.

An observer located in New York City on June 09, 1994 at 10pm, would see the moon, being 2% full, rising at 05:42 am and setting at 09:28 pm.

The previous full moon was on May 25, 1994 while the next full moon would come on Jun 23, 1994.

What is special about June 9th?

June 9th refers to a specific date on the calendar, which is the 9th day of the month of June. It is a date that occurs annually and is part of the Gregorian calendar, which is widely used around the world.

Over the years several events happened on June 9th, such as:

2019 - A crane that fell onto an apartment building in dallas caused severe weather to result in at least one death and six other injuries.

2018 - According to pajhwok afghan news, the taliban announced a three-day eid ceasefire in afghanistan with afghan authorities. on thursday, president ashraf ghani declared a ceasefire between the taliban and government troops. it was effective from june 12-19.

2017 - 2017 tehran attacks: officials and thousands of people attend the funerals of victims. los angeles times - president hassan rouhani claims that the attacks were against democracy and peace.
